A massive convention hall filled with thousands of tiny silhouetted figures viewed from above, rendered in vibrant cyberpunk style with neon purple and electric blue lighting cutting through atmospheric haze. At the center, a towering holographic rocket ship ascends toward a digital moon, its trail fragmenting into streams of glowing data particles and chat bubbles. The ceiling dissolves into a starfield mixed with circuit board patterns, while giant floating screens around the perimeter display abstract collaborative network visualizations. The crowd creates organic wave patterns suggesting excitement and connection, their collective energy represented by luminous threads linking person to person across the vast space.
